_sText:
Welcome
There are many secrets in surf_cheb, which make the map even more fun. Make sure you find those. If you have any ideas for future releases, or find any bugs, please let me know on the email address below.

How To Install
Simply copy the maps and materials folder to your
C:\\Program Files\\Valve\\Steam\\SteamApps\\<name>\\counter-strike source\\cstrike
folder.

Credits
Credits go to Nitro for beta testing the map for me, finding bugs and giving me ideas. Also Anomaly for running the cheb surf server, and allowing me to create a map after the server.

If you need any further help, add me to msn hypz_@hotmail.co.uk or send me an email.
